#: addons/win_cond_military_influence.wad/functions.lua:479 input:479 standard
msgid "The End is Near!"
msgstr "Dat Enn is nah!"

#: addons/win_cond_military_influence.wad/functions.lua:543 input:543 standard
msgid "Side quest: Conquer the whole map area"
msgstr "Sieden-Upgaav: Nimm de hele Kaart in"

#: addons/win_cond_military_influence.wad/functions.lua:545 input:545 standard
msgid ""
"Conquer the whole area of the map as fast as you can. It only counts if you "
"guard it too: the sum of the conquer areas of military sites has to be 120% "
"of the owned area."
msgstr ""
"Nimm so fix as du kannst dat hele Kaart-Gewest in. Dat tellt blots, wenn du "
"’t ok schüttst: De Summ vun de Innehmens-Gewesten vun Soldateree-Boen mutt "
"120% vun de eegen Kuntrei bedragen."

#: addons/win_cond_military_influence.wad/functions.lua:548 input:548 standard
msgid "Map conquered"
msgstr "Kaart innohmen"

#: addons/win_cond_military_influence.wad/functions.lua:549 input:549 standard
msgid "Congratulations! You have conquered the whole map."
msgstr "Glückwunsk! Du hest de hele Kaart innohmen."

#: addons/win_cond_military_influence.wad/functions.lua:585 input:585 standard
msgid "Side quest: Train heroes"
msgstr "Sieden-Upgaav: Bill Helden ut"

#: addons/win_cond_military_influence.wad/functions.lua:586 input:586 standard
#, lua-format
msgid "Train %d heroes as fast as you can."
msgstr "Bill so fix as du kannst %d Helden ut."

#: addons/win_cond_military_influence.wad/functions.lua:587 input:587 standard
msgid "Heroes trained"
msgstr "Helden utbillt"

#: addons/win_cond_military_influence.wad/functions.lua:588 input:588 standard
#, lua-format
msgid "Congratulations! You have trained %d heroes."
msgstr "Glückwunsk! Du hest %d Helden utbillt."

#: addons/win_cond_military_influence.wad/functions.lua:663 input:663 standard
#, lua-format
msgid ""
"Expand your territory, train your soldiers, and guard your territory with "
"military sites filled with heroes. You have to do all of them to get a "
"really good score. Highest score after %s wins."
msgstr ""
"Vergroter dien Gewest, bill diene Soldaten ut, un schütt dien Gewest mit "
"Soldateree-Boen vull mit Helden. Du muttst all deese Dingen doon, um eene "
"würrelk gode Weerttahl to kriegen. De hoogste Weerttahl na %s winnt."

#: addons/win_cond_military_influence.wad/functions.lua:670 input:670 standard
msgid "Final Score"
msgstr "Enn-Weerttahl"

#: addons/win_cond_military_influence.wad/init.lua:8 input:8 standard
msgid ""
"Conquer as much land as you can and train as many and strong soldiers as you "
"can in the set time."
msgstr ""
"Nimm so vööl Land in, as du kannst, un bill so völe un so machtige Soldaten "
"ut, as du in de vörgeven Tied kannst."
